  "general_provisions": "This bill requires a county to accept and process a plan review application for a single-family dwelling on a qualifying parcel that is not part of a subdivision.",
  "hilighted_provisions": "This bill:<hr><ltbullet>defines terms;<hr><ltbullet>amends the purpose of a county's general land use authority to include protecting property rights;<hr><ltbullet>describes the circumstances under which a county is required to accept and process a plan review application for a single-family dwelling on a qualifying parcel; and<hr><ltbullet>makes technical and conforming changes.",
